- masthead do
  %h1 Play Minecraft with your friends

  %p
    We've made multiplayer Minecraft fast and easy.

  = link_to 'Sign up now, it\'s free', root_path(anchor: 'plans'), class: 'button'


= render partial: 'users/new_user', object: User.new

#plans
  %p You can play for <strong class="highlight">#{pluralize User::FREE_HOURS, 'hour', 'hours'} free</strong>, each month. We only have two other plans:

  %table
    %thead
      %tr.name
        %th.casual Casual
        %th.pro Pro
    %tbody
      %tr.price
        %td.casual $3.95 / mo
        %td.pro $9.95 / mo
      %tr.hours
        %td.casual 80 hrs / mo
        %td.pro <em>Infinity</em> hours
      %tr.worlds
        %td.casual 1 world
        %td.pro <em>Infinity</em> worlds
      %tr.players
        %td.casual 4 Minefold players
        %td.pro <em>Infinity</em> Minefold players


%ol#features
  %li.feature
    %h2 Zen Simplicity
    %p We do it all for you. <strong>No more servers</strong>, RAM, Java, SSH or any of that mumbojumbo. Just sign up and play, grasshopper.

  %li.feature
    %h2 Show off
    %p We give you <strong>high quality maps</strong> of your worlds so you can quickly show your bros that rad 'coaster you've been working on.

  %li.feature
    %h2 Infinite worlds
    %p Unlike other Minecraft hosts, we let you create <strong>as many worlds as you like</strong>. Start a new one for every day of the week!

  %li.feature
    %h2 Realtime in-game chat
    %p See when your friends are playing online and chat with them straight from the site. You don't have to open Minecraft to shout <strong>“OMG”</strong>.

  %li.feature
    %h2 Make love, not grief
    %p Keep pesky griefers out by only inviting <strong>people you trust</strong> to play with you.

  %li.feature
    %h2 Peace of mind
    %p All your work is <strong>continiously backed up</strong> in multiple datacenters. Your builds are secure.

